Invocation Name: volunteer options
des: Would you like to help out in your community? There are many good organizations looking for volunteers like you. You'll find It can be rewarding and fun to volunteer! The Volunteer Options skill can get you started with a list of places to contact. To use this skill simply say Alexa, Ask Volunteer Options and she'll prompt you for the five digit zip code you are interested in.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
